9. Monetization
Phase 1 (Launch): Free beta. Email capture. Build user base and validate demand.
Phase 2 (Month 2-3): Freemium. Free tier with limited history. Pro at $9.99/mo for full access.
Phase 3 (Month 4+): Affiliate links to sportsbooks. Sponsored content from data providers. Premium tiers for institutional users.
Revenue Target
100 paying users at $9.99/mo = ~$1,000 MRR. This is the validation threshold.

